{"tid":2106573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再多一名入境處人員確診　灣仔上班負責後勤工作","createTime":"2020-07-13T12:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T13:54:21.000Z","uid":147522,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b3f20f6bd359ddcd232112e1083296d6a9f245","tid":2106573,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎持續爆發，據了解，入境處一名高級入境事務助理員，今日（13日）獲通知確診新冠肺炎。入境處表示，該名確診人員於灣仔入境事務大樓14及16樓負責後勤工作，該兩樓層並不是公眾樓層，不對外開放。<br />\n<br />\n他最近一次上班日期為7月10日，並於同日到診所求醫，隨即在今日傍晚獲通知確診。據悉，該其居所位於長沙灣，而其上班範圍經已全面消毒。"},{"pid":"44448b2a805b920b53ff2dea5836f9f305e0ddf3","tid":2106573,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"奶共啊嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290184ac729088f5bb8c0f32d3d644cbbd16ea7a","tid":2106573,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔WFH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4558f3c6850f1a5a7c9ad903817cdbad691f7156","tid":2106573,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e020ed67c7c410245247b9b3238aaaf5ef3e6161","tid":2106573,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"入境處人員確診係咪意味啲咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}